# PropFolio Global Standards

## Product Context

PropFolio is a greenfield iOS-first real estate investment intelligence app. The primary user promise is helping buyers feel confident they will make money on a property purchase.

## Platform Priorities

1. iOS-first, SwiftUI-first
2. Optimize for common iPhone sizes (iPhone 14/15/16 standard and Pro) before iPad or web
3. Clean, modern, premium but approachable visual language
4. Every screen must reinforce the core promise: confidence in making money

## Engineering Standards

### Financial Logic

- All financial formulas must be deterministic and fully unit-tested
- AI must never calculate financial metrics
- Never hide unsupported assumptions; surface them clearly in the UI

### Data Imports

- All external imports must record source, timestamp, and confidence level
- Keep expensive external API calls cached where possible
- Wrap every third-party API with an adapter layer
- Support partial-result fallback for all API imports

### Architecture

- Prefer modular files and small focused services/view models
- Every feature must handle all states: loading, empty, success, and error
- Expose data freshness and confidence visibly to users

### Quality Gates

- A reviewer subagent pass is required before any phase is considered complete
